gym.name: Jumping Jack
gym.descrip: A standing person jumps to a position with the legs and arms spread out and then jumps back to the original position.

gym.descrip: A heart-opening backbend that stretches your entire upper body

gym.name: Chest Stretch
gym.descrip: With the side of your body facing a wall, place your left palm on the wall.

gym.name: Russian Twist
gym.descrip: Aitting with your legs bent and your lower back straight

gym.name: Plank
gym.descrip: A long, narrow, flat piece of wood or similar material, of the type used for making floors

gym.name: Arm Raises
